COULD YOU BE OUR LUCAS? 

The Brookside Theatre, Romford are urgently looking for a male identifying musical theatre performer (playing age 18-25) to play the role of Lucas Beineke in THE ADDAMS FAMILY this Halloween.

This is a great role for a male performer in a fun musical.

Rehearsals are in Romford weekday evenings and Sundays by a schedule.

Show week w/c 27th Oct 2025

Please note this is an unpaid charity production

If you can help please either PM me pr email casting@brooksidetheatre.com

#castingcall #casting #musicaltheatre #addamsfamilymusical

items.text:
**Casting Call - Cornwall based Talent **

I'm producing a suite of social ads for a food hamper brand and casting talent for photography and video assets. 

We are looking to replicate people from all walks of life, celebrating the sweet life moments with a range of hamper gifts.

**Talent Requirements**
* Between 30 and 50
* Any gender, race, ability.
* Must have basic modelling and basic experience
* These are non speaking roles, but you must be comfortable acting out sequences, such as receiving a gift, opening the door to a package, etc.

**Please note: applicants MUST be based in the South Cornwall area and within a reasonable commute from our location in Praa Sands. **

**Filming: **Praa Sands, Thursday 16th October.  Beach front home location.

**Payment**

**Pays £350 for the day **(this fee includes the BSF and 1 year usage for paid social and web use)

Travel expenses up to £20 (with valid travel receipts), light breakfast and lunch is covered. 

**Please email giorgia@nusastudios.com **with your portfolio and headshot.

Thanks so much

Giorgia

items.text:
**$500 Finders Fee: Have You Been Ghosted By Your Husband Or Wife? (Docu-Series Casting)**

An acclaimed television production company and a major cable network are actively searching for women and men whose spouse has suddenly and mysteriously vanished, without warning, without explanation, and with no way to contact them. If you are still *legally married* but don’t know *where *your spouse is, you don’t have a clear explanation or *“why”* they left, or *how* to reach them, *we want to hear your story for a bold and empowering new series.*

**$500 Referral Fee: **Do You Know Someone? Share their information with us or simply have them tell us you referred them! Finders fee is paid IF referral is selected for production. 

*Selected for series candidates are compensated for taking part as well as receive expert help in tracking down their missing spouse, rebuilding their lives and finding closure. *

**To apply, please email: ****[casting@bodegapictures.com](mailto:casting@bodegapictures.com)****, **or visit: https://abandonedspouseshortapp.castingcrane.com/

items.text:
*OPEN CASTING CALL*
Recurring short form variety sketch series beginning late September in Los Angeles. 

Award-winning director of White Gaze (Blumhouse Patrons Circle recipient), Confluence (BAFTA and Oscar-qualifying film festivals), and upcoming sci-fi drama, Menstrual, and seasoned commercial and indie cinematographer are seeking actors for various roles and sketches. 

DM @etawashere on IG
if profile is private, please share headshot
(do NOT reply by FB messenger)

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'P.L. CINEMATIC SHORT FORM VARIETY SERIES FUSING GENRE, SATIRE, SATIRE.AN AND SINCERITY. THINK THINKATLANTA ATLANTA MEETS BARTHES MEETS MEETSINTERNET INTERNET CULTURE MEETS MUMBLECORE. OPENCALL LOSANGELES ANGEL NON-UNON/UNPAID JUNPAID ISO NATURALISTIC/ ACTING ADLIBABILITY ADLIB ABILITY COLLABORATIVESPIRIT SPIRIT NOEXPERIENCEREQUI REQUIRED SUBMISSIONS DM @ETA @ETAWASHERE ETA'

items.text:
Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius
+12022558377
Instagram: @deivjuo
YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

Hello, we are a group of students from Ngee Ann Poly Diploma in Filmmaking and we are looking for main talents for our short film.  
 
Title : Caregiver 
Genre : Shortfilm Drama 
Language : English/Malay 

Sypnosis : AN ELDERLY LADY SUFFERING FROM
DEMENTIA, LIVES HER LIFE DAILY,
UNAWARE OF THE TRUTH ABOUT HER
CAREGIVER SON

Location : TBC

RACE: MALAY
FAMILY ORIENTED

SON (ADAM): 
SCREENAGE: 30-45 Year Old 
RACE: MALAY
LOVING
CARING

Nurul (caregiver):

SCREENAGE: 25-30 Year Old 
RACE: Malay or able to speak/understand Malay  

 
CONTACT :

Contact details 
Age & Height 
Name  
Show reels (If you have any)

No acting experience is required and for the self audition video details, 
it will be sent to shortlisted applicants only. 
Thank you!

Familiar Faces Casting Call Short Fim Directed by: Daniela Aguirre DATE POSTED: 09-22-2025 POSSIBLE SHOOTING DATES: November 8th OR November 9th, 2025 Rehearsal dates: TBD Location: Chicago, IL
We are committed to diverse, inclusive casting. For every role, please submit qualifiec performers, without regard to disability, race, age, color, national origin, ethnic origin, sexua orientation, gender identity, or any other basis prohibited by law unless otherwise specifically indicated.
Logline : A college undergrad soaring to become a pediatric speech therapist is taunted by ar unexplainable nightmare that has gradually become worse over time.
Roles:
Katalina Desdemona (22) ( Portrayed female Lead) - A senior year college undergrad who grew up in an abusive houschold that impacted her by severely delaying her speech development. With ome help from her ELD teacher (English Language Development) Katalina was able to express herself more growing up and dreams of doing the same for others,
Young Katalina (7-9) (Portrayed female- lead)- Evil spirit who imitates the appearance o Katalina when she was younger. Who's seeking to collect her promised teeth.
Pierre Baker (22) (Portrayed male- supporting)- The loyal best friend of Katalina since 5" grade and who also took interest in studying for child development and literacy. Dedicated and nurturing best friend
If interested, available, or have questions email Daniela Aguirre Send headshots, resumes/reels 

to email: daguirre2@colum.edu

Deadline Date: October 24th. 2025
Compensation: Meal, Copy, Credit

sharedPost.text:
GWC is seeking people to portray 1960s White Upscale Gala Attendees (Ages 30-99) for upcoming A24 horror series MAMAS BOY

To submit, email mamasboy@gwcnyc.com with all the following info using the subject line
“IG Gala”

Full name

Are you a SAG-AFTRA member in good standing (include SAG number) or non-SAG

Phone number

Are you fully available for shoot on 10/9, 10/10 & a TBD fitting?

Please note current height, weight, clothing and shoe sizes*

Please note if you have any tattoos or piercings, and attach a photo

Are you comfortable around atmospheric smoke?

If 21+, are you comfortable smoking a herbal cigarette, if asked? (It’s ok if not)

Men: Are you comfortable being clean shaven for the shoot if needed?

Men & women: Are you comfortable receiving a 1960’s haircut on set, if needed?

Are you local to NJ/NY area?

Confirm you are 18 years or older

Attach current, clear photos (close-up and full body)

This background role is not covered by SAG-AFTRA CBA and subject to a preference of employment provision.

*Height, weight, and clothing sizes are used for costuming purposes only, unless needed for the casting of stand-ins or photodoubles.
Please note, you must be able to present valid identification to fill out a federal I-9 form and be paid.

#extras #gala #1960 #elegant #a24

**$500 Finders Fee: Have You Been Ghosted By Your Husband Or Wife? (Docu-Series Casting)**

An acclaimed television production company and a major cable network are actively searching for women and men whose spouse has suddenly and mysteriously vanished, without warning, without explanation, and with no way to contact them. If you are still *legally married* but don’t know *where *your spouse is, you don’t have a clear explanation or *“why”* they left, or *how* to reach them, *we want to hear your story for a bold and empowering new series.*

**$500 Referral Fee: **Do You Know Someone? Share their information with us or simply have them tell us you referred them! Finders fee is paid IF referral is selected for production. 

*Selected for series candidates are compensated for taking part as well as receive expert help in tracking down their missing spouse, rebuilding their lives and finding closure. *

**To apply, please email: ****[casting@bodegapictures.com](mailto:casting@bodegapictures.com)****, **or visit: https://abandonedspouseshortapp.castingcrane.com/

items.text:
Series - September 2025
Rejoinder: 5.5 - Script Breakdown: Identify Chemical Messengers

At the prompting of the brain, the sensory system (the five senses) import raw data (script) from the external environment (stage) into the internal environment. At the prompting of the brain, the mind synthesizes stimuli from the raw data received. At the prompting of the brain, the limbic system generates emotions in response to the synthesized stimuli. At the prompting of the brain, the skeletal and muscular systems express emotions as human behavior (dramatic performance).

At the prompting of the brain, chemical messengers facilitate or inhibit the transition of information between body parts. The release of chemical messengers operate in auto mode in real life situation, because the host human body has the internal intelligence base to facilitate it. It gets tricky in a dramatic performance situation in which the actor plays a character role. The actor delivers poor quality dramatic performance because she lacks the intelligence base capacity to the release process of chemical messengers. Just like sophisticated Artificial Intelligence (AI) processes require huge amount of electrical power to execute, chemical messengers require 'super duper' high quality intelligence base to process. If the actor could identify the chemical messengers required for a proposed dramatic performance, she could build up the necessary intelligence base to support it.

What do you think? This is a scientific approach to acting. I welcome a discussion for a better understanding. Feel free to express yourself with a question or a statement. There is so much to explore, thinking outside the box.

Note: Send me a message to join my subscription-based virtual scientific acting class.

Tickets are now available for our upcoming Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event, taking place on Sunday, October 26th.

 

Networking is essential for advancing your career in the industry, and Marble Academy for Drama and Management has proudly facilitated these events for years. With over 90 attendees, our June gathering was a tremendous success, and we are determined to build on that momentum.

 

You will have the opportunity to engage with accomplished actors, visionary directors, prominent producers, and skilled crew members who can offer valuable insights and possibly help bring your next project to life.

 

Think about it, if there were an event where you could connect with exceptionally talented cast and crew who could help bring your next project to life, wouldn’t you want to be there?

 

Take a look at this video from a previous event…..

www.youtube.com/watch?v=EM4jwjRxny4

 

So, join us on Sunday, October 26th, from 2 PM to 6:30 PM at HOME Mcr, located at 2 Tony Wilson Place, Manchester, M15 4FN.

 

Secure your tickets through this link:

www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239

 

I look forward to seeing you there!

Angela Boehm Casting is now looking for talent for a Promotional Video Shoot for 'OHIO JOBS'.

This project will be filming in October in Cleveland, OH, Columbus, OH, AND CINCINNATI, OH. (We have 18 Roles over 3 Different Cities).

Please read carefully below for details:

DETAILS:
- Project: 'OHIO JOBS' Promotional Shoot
- Project Location: Cleveland, OH (TBD) / Columbus, OH (TBD) / Cincinnati, OH (TBD)
- Date(s): October 7th / October 8th / October 9th / October 10th
- CALLBACK Date: Tuesday, September 30th (via Zoom)
- Rate: $500/10hr +20% per Session.
- Fitting Rate: $50/hr + 20% 
(Cincinnati Talent will fit on OCTOBER 6th. Columbus & Cleveland Talent will fit ON-SET)
- Usage: 2-Year Usage Buyout $2500 + 20% (Broadcast, Digital, Social, Print, OOH, Industrial)

WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR:
WE HAVE 18 ROLES OVER THE 3 OHIO CITIES FOR ALL AGES AND ETHNICITIES!!

Link to Roles & Cities they film: https://bit.ly/OhioJobsROLESandCITIES

SUBMISSION / AUDITION INSTRUCTIONS:
- Please email all auditions to: angela@angelaboehmcasting.com

- Deadline for Auditions is 9:00am on FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 26th.

- SUBJECT LINE: OHIO JOBS Audition / (Your Name)
- Please have a blank background (DO NOT film outside).
- Please slate at the end of the audition (Slate can be in a separate video).

Slate Requirements:
- Full Name
- Agent (Phone number if you do not have an Agent)
- Location (PLEASE SLATE IF YOU'RE WILLING TO WORK LOCAL IN MORE THAN ONE OF THE MENTIONED CITIES)
- Please include in your slate a close-up of BOTH of your hands, FRONT & BACK!
- PLEASE SLATE ANY CONFLICTS ON FILMING/FITTING/CALLBACK DATES
- Please send the audition via Dropbox Folder or via WeTransfer Link (PLEASE MAKE SURE WE HAVE PERMISSION TO OPEN YOUR FILE).

Click below for the Audition Sides:
Link to Sides: https://bit.ly/OhioJobsSIDES

Kind regards,
Angela Boehm Casting Team

PLEASE NOTE: This is just a submission. If you are booked, we will reach out to YOU.

🕒 Time: 2pm - 6pm
🎬 Project Type: Independent Feature Film (non-union)
💰 Compensation: unpaid/IMDb Credit/meal provided

Age Range - 18-Late 20s
Gender - Any gender 

This will be the science fair scene so we are looking for men and women to play college students. Come dressed up like you’re in the 80s going to school.

Requirements:
- Must be local to Seattle, WA
- Comfortable being on camera for background action
- Must provide own wardrobe in 80s style ex. (casual school attire)

Send an email to darecarri2@gmail.com the director with the subject line: “Extras – [Your Name]” and include:
• Full name
• Age & height
• Recent photo (clear, natural, no filters)
• Contact info (phone & email)
• Availability for listed date

This will be the science fair scene so we are looking for men and women to play college students. Come dressed up like you’re in the 80s going to school.

Requirements:
- Must be local to Seattle, WA
- Comfortable being on camera for background action
- Must provide own wardrobe in 80s style ex. (casual school attire)

To Submit:
Send an email to darecarri2@gmail.com the director with the subject line: “Extras – [Your Name]” and include:
• Full name
• Age & height
• Recent photo (clear, natural, no filters)
• Contact info (phone & email)
• Availability for listed date

This will be a fun opportunity to be part of an indie feature film! Great for experience and networking. Meals and credit provided. We look forward to working with you!

Rosenteatret inviterer til audition på det velkendte og elskede stykke “Svend, Knud, og Valdemar”, historien om de tre danske konger… Eller faktisk er det mere en humoristisk historie om en skuespillertrup der prøver at sætte stykket op, men ALT går galt for dem 😆

Så er du klar på at få folk i salen til at grine over dine fjollerier, men kan du også spille seriøst, så er der lige præcis DIG vi mangler! 

PRAKTISK INFORMATION
- Tidspunkt: d. 29/9 kl. 19
- Sted: Rosenteatret (Teatertorvet 1, 8000 Århus C).
- Tilmelding: Skriv til lisbetlautrup@hotmail.com.

Auditionen foregår som en gruppeaudition, hvor i skal forberede jer hjemmefra på at fremføre første vers af “Jeg ved en lærkerede”, og efterfølgende får i tildelt nogle tekster i skal fremføre.

Hvis du ik kender stykket, kan vi anbefale at se det på YouTube ✨

Thomas

+++ Kompars:innen gesucht für Debüt-Kinofilm „DIE MATRIARCHIN“ (AT) von Alison Kuhn +++

📆 14.10.2025 in Berlin

🏙 Motiv: Fußgängerzone – Schüler:innen auf dem Weg nach Hause

💶 Tagesgage: 80€ bis maximal 6h (+45min Pause)

Wir suchen noch junge Komparserie wohnhaft in Berlin im Alter von 18-21 Jahren! Zeitlich voraussichtlich 8 bis 13:00 Uhr!

Inhalt: Die 17-jährige Kim muss sich ihre Plattenbauwohnung an der deutschen Ostsee nicht nur mit ihrer vietnamesischen Mutter und ihrem kleinen Bruder Bao teilen, sondern auch mit jeder Menge wildfremden Vietnames:innen. Die Mutter betreibt in ihrem kleinen Brautmodeladen eine Agentur für illegale Schleusungen aus Vietnam nach Europa. Kim möchte mit allen Mitteln ihrer Mutter gefallen und eines Tages die Agentur übernehmen. Als sich endlich eine Chance ergibt, wird sie sich schnell bewusst, was das wirklich für sie bedeutet.

Es ist keine Vorerfahrung nötig! 🎬

Meldet euch mit KOMPARSERIE BERLIN im Betreff, Fotos von euch an:

📩 diematriarchin.extras@gmail.com

items.text:
**Hey ihr Lieben 👋,**

wir sind eine junge **Supplement-Marke aus Deutschland** und suchen **UGC Creatorinnen** für spannende Projekte 🇩🇪🎥

👉 Gesucht sind:
* deutschsprachige, junge Creatorinnen (idealerweise U30)
* sportlich, kreativ und selbstbewusst vor der Kamera
* Erfahrung mit **authentischen Handyaufnahmen** (Talking Head Clips, kurze Story-Videos etc.)

Wir schicken dir unser Produkt zu und du erstellst:
* **Talking Head Videos**
* **individuelle Clips** für Social Media

💸 Das Projekt ist **bezahlt** und bei guter Zusammenarbeit sind **regelmäßige Folgeaufträge** sehr wahrscheinlich!

Wenn du Interesse hast:
➡️ Kommentiere unter diesem Beitrag oder schreib mir eine DM ✨

🎅 **Poszukiwany Święty Mikołaj do Bombkolandii!** 🎅

Szukamy osoby, która wcieli się w rolę Świętego Mikołaja w magicznym świecie **Bombkolandii**.
📅 Praca w terminie: **12 listopada – 19 grudnia**

👦👧 Kogo szukamy?
* Osoby komunikatywnej i otwartej, która potrafi nawiązać dobry kontakt z dziećmi.
* Kogoś, kogo pytania dzieci nie zaskoczą i kto potrafi z uśmiechem odpowiadać na ich dociekliwe rozmowy.
* Osoby serdecznej, przyjaznej i charyzmatycznej, która sprawi, że spotkanie z Mikołajem będzie niezapomnianym przeżyciem.
* Mile widziane **doświadczenie w pracy jako Święty Mikołaj**.
* Osoby, która potrafi **zapanować nad grupą dzieci** i utrzymać świąteczną atmosferę podczas spotkania.

✨ Oferujemy:
* Pracę w wyjątkowej, świątecznej atmosferze,
* Niezapomniane doświadczenie i radość ze spotkań z dziećmi,
* **Zapewniamy kompletny strój Świętego Mikołaja**.

📍 **Bombkolandia znajduje się we wsi Głęboczyca, gmina Dobre, powiat miński.**

📩 CV prosimy przesyłać na adres: **damentka.tomasz@gmail.com**

Dołącz do Bombkolandii i spraw dzieciom prawdziwą radość! 🎄🎁

Whether you're just starting or want to improve the talent you already have, Marble Academy in Swinton, Manchester, will help unlock your full potential and refine your craft to help capture the attention of casting directors in film, television, and theatre.

 

Here’s why you should seize this incredible opportunity:

**Renowned Excellence**: Marble Academy is not only celebrated by Spotlight as one of the premier drama academies in the country, but is also the recipient of the **Manchester & North West Prestige Awards **for **Theatre School Of The Year**.
Here, you won’t just learn; you’ll train with one of the best in the business!

 

**Authentic Training**: Our L.A.M.D.A.-qualified tutor, Christian Le Feuvre, brings a wealth of real-world experience that empowers you to delve deeply into characters and scenes. His insightful feedback doesn’t just boost your confidence; it ignites your growth as an actor, providing you with a fresh perspective on every script. With his nurturing and constructive coaching style, you’ll be amazed at how he can transform your journey as an actor.

 

But don’t just take our word for it—explore the glowing reviews and dive into our programme details for a closer look at what we offer at www.marbleacademy.co.uk

 

Audition dates are still available!

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

items.text:
Hi Everyone!

I'm a student studying filmmaking at **Birmingham City University**, and for one of our assignments, we are creating a **short film** and are looking for actors.

The concept isn't decided yet, but we are deciding between two:
1. A past chess champion reminisces about his glory days and replays the match that he lost in which started his downfall.
2. A girl whose inner self is screaming at her to help, while she is sucked into her phone, a film themed on how addicted we are to our phones.

We have a Test Shoot Day on the 23rd of October, 9:00am-12:00pm, and the Shoot Day is on the 4th of November, 9:00am-4:00pm. Both are at Parkside Building, Birmingham City University.

As we are students, this will be unpaid, unfortunately. But this is a great opportunity for actors who are starting out and want to get something on their resumes. We will include you in the credits.

We will have more details before the shoot, so don't worry.

If you are interested, please send an email to this address: **maisie.condron@mail.bcu.ac.uk**

Please include this information:

- Name

- Age

- Sex

- Location

- A self-tape of any performance

We will also be having more films come up in the future, so if you don't fit any of the roles described, you can still send an application in!

Thank you!

Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius
+12022558377
Instagram: @deivjuo
YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

items.text:
Connor Knowles is a passionate model and actor based in Derby, United Kingdom. With a background in social media. Hosting boxing events, and promoting, he has developed a versatile skill set that allows him to thrive in both the modelling and acting realms. 

Having currently not worked with any clothing brands but looking to work with many brands and appearing in projects such as Rise of the Footsoldier: Retribution as a supporting actor, and recently featured in a YouTube video for the content creator MystroYNL in a video called “Guess the Black Person”, he is known for his ability to bring characters to life with authenticity and grace. He’s always looking to work with anyone and further develop his character and personal brand. 

In addition to his modelling and acting work, Connor Knowles is very versatile and talented and has the ability to create a unique style and personality to his work, which enhances his performances. When not in front of the camera, he enjoys creating content on social media, promoting his work, and sharing his creativity with others. While also engaging in his own personal creative ventures which reflect on his vibrant personality. 

For inquiries, please contact via connorleeknowles04@gmail.com or his social media handles @CKnowlesUK/@CKnowlesUK_

sharedPost.text:
🎅 **Poszukiwany Święty Mikołaj do Bombkolandii!** 🎅

Szukamy osoby, która wcieli się w rolę Świętego Mikołaja w magicznym świecie **Bombkolandii**.
📅 Praca w terminie: **12 listopada – 19 grudnia**

👦👧 Kogo szukamy?
* Osoby komunikatywnej i otwartej, która potrafi nawiązać dobry kontakt z dziećmi.
* Kogoś, kogo pytania dzieci nie zaskoczą i kto potrafi z uśmiechem odpowiadać na ich dociekliwe rozmowy.
* Osoby serdecznej, przyjaznej i charyzmatycznej, która sprawi, że spotkanie z Mikołajem będzie niezapomnianym przeżyciem.
* Mile widziane **doświadczenie w pracy jako Święty Mikołaj**.
* Osoby, która potrafi **zapanować nad grupą dzieci** i utrzymać świąteczną atmosferę podczas spotkania.

✨ Oferujemy:
* Pracę w wyjątkowej, świątecznej atmosferze,
* Niezapomniane doświadczenie i radość ze spotkań z dziećmi,
* **Zapewniamy kompletny strój Świętego Mikołaja**.

📍 **Bombkolandia znajduje się we wsi Głęboczyca, gmina Dobre, powiat miński.**

📩 CV prosimy przesyłać na adres: **damentka.tomasz@gmail.com**

Dołącz do Bombkolandii i spraw dzieciom prawdziwą radość! 🎄🎁

**[PAID CASTING CALL]**

We’re looking for warm and friendly Singaporeans who commute regularly by public transport to be part of our upcoming social media content.

📍 Shoot period: 29 Sept – 03 Oct (final date will be confirmed with selected talents)
⏱ Time commitment: 3-4 hours
💵 Talent fee: $100 per talent

**Who we need:**
Friendly individuals who are comfortable on camera (no acting experience required!) and who use public transport often, whether it’s commuting to work, visiting family, or exploring new places.

**Roles available:**

1.       1x Senior (50–65 years old) – Preferably a warm, motherly figure who uses public transport regularly

2.       1x Junior (7–12 years old) – Expressive and comfortable in front of the camera

3.       3x Young Adults – Preferably a group of friends, with at least one being a Person with Disability (PWD)

4.       1x Working Adult (25–35 years old) – Someone who travels across multiple train lines and at least 10 stations each way for work or daily routine

 

**Important:** We’re looking for Singaporean nationalities for this project only.

If you're really interested, please **WhatsApp** your profile to Joyce +6580660556 with the following details:
Name per IC:
Contact number:
Email address:
DOB:
Nationality:
Home Address:

items.text:
📣 [PAID CASTING CALL | SINGAPORE]

Studio Ikura is casting a family with one child 👨‍👩‍👧 for a shopping mall commercial highlighting lifestyle and family-friendly experiences 🛍✨.

🎬 Shoot Details

🗓 Date: 13th or 14th October 2025 (TBC)

⏰ Duration: Full day (8–10 hours)

💵 Compensation: SGD $1,500 (all-in, for the entire family)

⏳ Payment Terms: Within 30 days after the shoot

👨‍👩‍👧 Role Required

Family with One Child (any ethnicity, genuine warmth and chemistry preferred)

👨 Father (25–40 yrs old)

👩 Mother (25–40 yrs old)

🧒 Child (4–10 yrs old, boy or girl)

Total Family Fee: SGD $1,500

📌 Requirements & Notes

✅ Only real families will be considered (to ensure authentic on-camera chemistry)

🇸🇬 Singapore-based

🎥 Comfortable on camera with natural, relaxed expressions

👗 Wardrobe guidance will be provided (casual, stylish looks suitable for a shopping environment)

💰 The fee is all-inclusive (no additional loading fees will be applied)

📺 Usage: footage may be used in perpetuity across the developer’s marketing platforms

📩 Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted. Shortlisted families will also be asked to submit a short self-filmed family video for casting purposes.

✉️ How to Apply

Please email mitchellcastingcall@gmail.com with:

Names, ages, and ethnicity of all family members

Recent family photos + individual headshot and side profile

Contact details

Availability on 13th or 14th October 2025

🙌 Looking forward to hearing from you all!

**STATYŚCI - Dzieci i dorośli do popularnego serialu kryminalnego.**
**Gdańsk/Kwidzyn 30.09.2025r.**

*Poszukujemy dzieci oraz dorosłych w każdym wieku do udziału w nagraniach scen dożynek w popularnym serialu kryminalnym. To doskonała okazja, aby zobaczyć od kulis pracę planu filmowego i wziąć udział w wyjątkowej produkcji telewizyjnej.*
 
**Nie wymagamy doświadczenia aktorskiego.**
**Termin:** 30 września 2025r.
 
**Oferujemy:**
- wynagrodzenie w wysokości 110 zł (płatne gotówką po planie),
- zapewniony transport z Gdańska i Kwidzyna w obie strony.
     
**Zgłoszenia prosimy przesyłać na adres:** casting@sceneria.com.pl

**W treści zgłoszenia należy podać:**

    - imię i nazwisko,
     
    - miasto zamieszkania,
     
    - wiek,
     
    - numer telefonu,
     
    - aktualne zdjęcie,
     
    - informację o transporcie: własny / Gdańsk / Kwidzyn.

**Jeśli jeszcze nie współpracujesz z Nami kliknij w link poniżej**
📌 Rejestracja online (dla nowych użytkowników): [https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie)

***Casting jest otwarty dla wszystkich zainteresowanych – nie wymagamy wcześniejszego doświadczenia przed kamerą.***

items.text:
‼Halo Łódź i okolice‼
#**ZAPRASZAMYNAPLAN **📽🎥‼‼

Serdecznie zapraszamy do udziału w
kontynuacji kultowego serialu, dla jednej z platform streamingowych. Plan
będzie wyjazdowy (ok. 100 km), na miejscu gramy pod dachem. Można się zapisywać
na 1, 2 lub 3 dni. 

✅ **KIEDY i GDZIE:**
Wyjazd z ŁODZI (oczywiście powrót w to samo
miejsce, pkt. zbiórki będzie dopiero ustalony).
**30.09 (wt.), 01.10 (śr.), 03.10 (pt.)** ➡ kobiety i mężczyźni.

❇ **ZAPRASZAMY: **🧍‍♀️🧍
Panie i Panów, o każdej możliwej aparycji, w
wieku +16 lat, górnej granicy wieku brak - liczą się chęci i pozytywne🕵
nastawienie do udziału w planie zdjęciowym.

💰**WYNAGRODZENIE **💲 za udział w planie: 100 zł netto/dzień zdjęciowy (UoD, płatne przelewem) + dodatkowo 20 zł netto za podróż tam i z powrotem (Produkcyjnym autokarem ). 🙂

Na planie Produkcja zapewnia: kawę, herbatę,
wodę, bułki i jednodaniowy obiad. A także opiekę medyczną.
—
⬇ **KOMPLETNE ZGŁOSZENIE** zawierające poniższe dane, wyślij:
- komunikatorem WhatsApp/SMS na nr ‪+48 660
543 967;
- lub mailem, z tytułem: „Odjazdowa ŁÓDŹ”:
123cast.film@gmail.com

**‼W mailu / komunikatorze podaj wszystkie**
**poniższe dane, dokładnie wg. tej formatki ⬇:**
—
Imię i nazwisko
Nr tel.
Miejsce zamieszkania
Data urodzenia
Wzrost (w cm)
Waga (w kg)
Rozm. obuwia (w nr EU)
—
Terminy w których mógł(a)byś wziąć udział w
planie filmowym (30.09, 01.10, 03.10).
—
+dołącz koniecznie jako ZAŁĄCZNIK DO MAILA
(bez linku do galerii zdjęć)/wiadomości na WhatsApp:
2x AKTUALNE ZDJĘCIA, zrobione telefonem
komórkowym -> portret i sylwetka: z aktualną fryzurą i wyglądem (zrobione
max. do 3 dni przed ich wysłaniem); bez osób trzecich na zdjęciach, i bez
nakryć głowy oraz bez okularów.
—
Do zobaczenia na planie :)

items.text:
Welcome to our Warsaw Impact Community!

We’re growing fast, and we’re excited to have you here. Whether you’re a passionate crowd member, an art lover who wants to connect with the artists you see on stage, or a creative looking to network, this is your place.

If you’re an aspiring artist thinking about how to earn money from your craft and take the leap into becoming a full-time creative, you’ll find support, ideas, and inspiration here. This community is all about connection, creativity, and growth.

Together we learn, share, and improve as artists through exclusive workshops, meetups, live shows, festivals, and more, crucially, we’re building a space where the right people can discover you. Actors, musicians, and performers in our community are regularly seen by casting agents, talent scouts, and industry professionals who come to our events looking for fresh talent. If you want exposure, meaningful industry connections, and a real chance to be discovered, this is the place to be.

We’re glad you’ve joined us, get ready to perform, connect, and be seen.

🌐 impactwarsaw.com

Telegram group: https://t.me/+BGl_Q7Qg5wI4NTY0

Instagram: @impactfestwarsaw

Hi everyone, I'm Deividas 30, Lithuanian.

Model | Performer | Wellness Professional
With over 50 professional photoshoots under my belt — including paid projects across fashion, lifestyle, artistic, body paint, and life modeling — I have developed a versatile presence in front of the camera backed by a disciplined lifestyle and unique skillset.

Link below intro video
https://drive.google.com/file/d/19OcejTSRFWF2ZmQxdeoF92CEF7TKKAdb/view?usp=drivesdk

Alongside modeling, I bring on-screen experience from multiple TV shows, interview formats, podcasts, and extra appearances in my home country, while continuously expanding into acting and performance-based work.

Performance Skills
• Aerial Acrobatics — Hoop, Trapeze, Silks, Rope (Beginner–Intermediate)
• Contact Fire Staff — Intermediate
• Katana Wielding — Intermediate 
• Yoga — Advanced
• Swimming — Advanced
• Parkour - Intermediate
• Dancing - non professional but confident dancer

I’m currently seeking freelance work as model/actor/performer and agency representation (available internationally). Open to test shoots, collaborations, and paid opportunities.

✨ Updated measurements (as of Sept 22, 2025):
Height: 195cm
Chest: 41
Waist: 32
Hips: 37.5
Neck: 16
Sleeve: 32 (81.5cm)
Inseam: 32 (81.5cm)
Outseam: 36.4 (92.3cm)
Shoulder Width: 19 (48.5cm)
Shoe: UK 10.5 (can do 10–11) | EU 44–46

🌍 Based in London | Available worldwide

Professional Background
• Qualified Swimming Coach, Yoga Teacher, and Personal Trainer with 12+ years of teaching experience.
• Deep expertise in health, movement, breath, wellness, and high performance.

What Sets Me Apart
• Strong work ethic, relentless discipline, and ability to perform under discomfort, pressure, and challenging conditions.
• Holistic approach to self-regulation — always camera-ready, physically prepared, mentally sharp, and adaptable.
• Highly motivated in building my craft and presence — I create, edit, and post content daily across YouTube, TikTok, and Instagram to develop audience reach and on-camera charisma.

Current Focus
Seeking opportunities in modeling, acting, and performance — primarily in the UK (based in London ) but open to international projects. I’m committed to levelling up my skills, embracing bold creative challenges, and bringing exceptional authentic energy, professionalism, and reliability to every collaboration.

If you need anything else please let me know 

Kindest regards 
Deividas Juozapavičius

YouTube: @deivjuo
TikTok: @deivjuo

items.text:
Hi Everyone!

I'm a student studying filmmaking at **Birmingham City University**, and for one of our assignments, we are creating a **short film** and are looking for actors.

The concept isn't decided yet, but we are deciding between two:
1. A past chess champion reminisces about his glory days and replays the match that he lost in which started his downfall.
2. A girl whose inner self is screaming at her to help, while she is sucked into her phone, a film themed on how addicted we are to our phones.

We have a Test Shoot Day on the 23rd of October, 9:00am-12:00pm, and the Shoot Day is on the 4th of November, 9:00am-4:00pm. Both are at Parkside Building, Birmingham City University.

As we are students, this will be unpaid, unfortunately. But this is a great opportunity for actors who are starting out and want to get something on their resumes. We will include you in the credits.

We will have more details before the shoot, so don't worry.

If you are interested, please send an email to this address: **maisie.condron@mail.bcu.ac.uk**

Please include this information:

- Name

- Age

- Sex

- Location

- A self-tape of any performance

We will also be having more films come up in the future, so if you don't fit any of the roles described, you can still send an application in!

Thank you!

items.text:
🎬 Набор танцоров на сезон 2026 в развлекательный парк Samsung Everland 에버랜드 (withEverland) (Южная Корея, г. Йонин)

✨ График отбора:

 • 1-й этап (подача документов): до 2 ноября (вс)

 • 2-й этап (доп. документы для прошедших 1-й этап): до 16 ноября (вс)

 • Окончательный отбор: конец ноября

🎯 Кого мы ищем:

 • Жанры: балет / джаз-дэнс / стрит-дэнс / спортивный танец / паркур / акробатика / ролики

 • Особые навыки: приветствуется сочетание танца и специальных навыков

 • Требования: опыт работы в выбранной сфере от 1 года и профильное образование

 • Рост:

 • Мужчины: 178–190 см

 • Женщины: 165–175 см

 • Кандидаты европейской внешности

 

💰 Оплата:

 • До вычета налогов: 2,156,880 KRW

🏠 Что предоставляется:

 • Перелёт в обе стороны

 • Проживание в общежитии (по 1 человеку в комнате)

 • Двухразовое питание (выбор: корейское / международное меню)

📄 Документы для подачи:

 • 1-й этап:

 • Профиль (форма ENT)

 • Видео с самопрезентацией (снято после 25 сентября)

 • Видео с авторской хореографией (до 2 видео)

 • Референс-видео (до 2 видео) (видео с выступлений/шоу)

 • Фотографии (полный рост / лицо / сцена)

 • Указать языки, которыми владеете

 • Для роликов/акробатики/спецнавыков – обязательно указать

 • 2-й этап:

 • Видео с назначенной хореографией (только для прошедших 1-й этап)

📌 Для подачи заявки:

Заполняйте форму по ссылке и прикрепляйте фото и видео.

Hey everyone . Take a look at our post below and message us The Foundry Acting Studio if you’re ready to take your career to the next step .

Trust me . It’s worth a read. 

Have a wonderful day and much love and respect to you all

sharedPost.text:
The Foundry Acting Studio

Where Professional Training Meets Real Opportunity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe every actor deserves a world class education without barriers, hidden costs, or false promises.

Our curriculum…. built and refined over six years,  is internationally recognised, exceeding Spotlight’s accreditation requirements by more than three times. We are Spotlight approved, SAG recognised, and currently in talks with other major organisations worldwide. Our work is supported by acclaimed writers, directors, and actors connected to some of the most influential platforms in the industry.

What makes us different:
 • World Class Curriculum: Designed to equal the top schools in the world, yet offered at a fraction of the cost.
 • No Hidden Tiers or Costs: Every actor receives the same training. There are no “higher levels,” upsells, or paywalls. Your talent is never defined by your wallet.
 • Personal Coaching: We keep classes small, so every actor is seen, heard, and individually assessed with hands on guidance.
 • No Agency Agenda: We are not an agency. You will never pay us for a promise of representation. Our focus is training and opportunity, not commission.
 • Industry Films: We are the only UK studio guaranteeing work by producing industry standard films with RED and ARRI cameras…. work that goes directly on your Spotlight profile.
 • Equality & Integrity

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we believe in building the industry, not dividing it. For that reason, we do not accept students who are currently in the middle of a paid term with another school or who are tied to an agency that is directly run by that same school. We respect the work of fellow coaches and do not believe in poaching actors away from their commitments.

Once an actor has completed their term elsewhere and is no longer represented under an agency attached to another school, they are welcome to join us for a fresh start. This ensures absolute fairness, integrity, and clarity for everyone involved.

Because The Foundry is not an agency, your place with us is never tied to representation. When you train here, your development is entirely about your craft. If you do not currently have an agent, our team will guide you toward finding one that best suits your path, independent, professional representation that has nothing to do with paying for classes.

We believe this creates a healthier, more transparent industry for all… actors, coaches, and agencies alike.

 • Accessibility: Whether you are working full-time, on benefits, retired, or just beginning your journey, our training is affordable and inclusive. Discounts are available for civil servants.
 • Expanding Opportunities: Teen classes are launching soon, and new locations are opening across the UK.

Our Philosophy

When you walk through our doors, you are not a number, not a “pound sign,” and never a currency. You are an actor, with equal right to professional training, opportunity, and growth.

At The Foundry, we believe in community. We believe in supporting fellow actors, fellow coaches, headshot photographers, showreel specialists, fight choreographers, and everyone who contributes to the craft. Together, we build the industry.

Ready to Join?

Direct message us today for full details on class times, dates, and locations near you. Step into a studio that is reshaping the future of acting in the UK and beyond.

The Foundry Acting Studio
Professional. Inclusive. Respected. Recognised

items.text:
Tickets are now available for our upcoming Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event, taking place on Sunday, October 26th.

 

Networking is essential for advancing your career in the industry, and Marble Academy for Drama and Management has proudly facilitated these events for years. With over 90 attendees, our June gathering was a tremendous success, and we are determined to build on that momentum.

 

You will have the opportunity to engage with accomplished actors, visionary directors, prominent producers, and skilled crew members who can offer valuable insights and possibly help bring your next project to life.

 

Think about it, if there were an event where you could connect with exceptionally talented cast and crew who could help bring your next project to life, wouldn’t you want to be there?

 

Take a look at this video from a previous event…..

www.youtube.com/watch?v=EM4jwjRxny4

 

So, join us on Sunday, October 26th, from 2 PM to 6:30 PM at HOME Mcr, located at 2 Tony Wilson Place, Manchester, M15 4FN.

 

Secure your tickets through this link:

www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239

 

I look forward to seeing you there!

items.text:
**Twój głos to Twoja tożsamość.**
Nie tylko brzmienie – ale **energia, obecność i wpływ**, które zostają w głowie i poruszają serca.

Cześć, jestem **Edyta** –
aktorka, mentorka neurokomunikacji i psychologii głosu.
Twórczyni metody **3E: Energia – Emocja – Ekspresja**.

Na co dzień pomagam liderom, ekspertom i przedsiębiorcom, którzy **już mają wiedzę i doświadczenie**, ale:

❌ ich wystąpienia są tylko „poprawne”
❌ głos brzmi płasko, niewyraźnie, bez przebicia
❌ trema i stres zabierają im siłę i spójność przekazu

Wydobywam z nich **mocny, głęboki głos**, który **prowadzi, inspiruje i zostawia ślad**.
To głos, który **nie musi być głośny – by był słyszany.**
Głos, który mówi z **dystynkcją, spokojem i magnetyczną pewnością siebie.**

**Pracuję z głosem na trzech poziomach:**
✅ Magnetyczna pewność siebie
✅ Charyzma i autorytet
✅ Głos jako narzędzie wpływu i transformacji – by mówić tak, by **prowadzić, poruszać i zostawać w pamięci.**

To właśnie esencja mojej metody 3E.
Bo **autorytet nie krzyczy. Autorytet mówi z wagą.**
Pomagam Ci **wyrazić siebie – z klarownością, emocją i siłą.**
Twój przekaz ma znaczenie. Pomogę Ci powiedzieć go tak, by **trafiał prosto w sedno.**

**Program „Głos Autorytetu” to nie kurs.**
To **transformacja osobowości scenicznej** – od wewnętrznych blokad do magnetycznej ekspresji.

✅ Mówisz z autorytetem
✅ Przemawiasz z ciała, nie z lęku
✅ Twój głos staje się narzędziem obecności i wpływu

📅 Nowa edycja rusza w październiku
🔒 Miejsca są ograniczone – to kameralna, ekskluzywna grupa
💌 Jeśli czujesz, że to Twój czas – napisz do mnie prywatnie na messenger lub mailowo: edyta.nestorowicz@gmail.com

**Mów spokojnie. Mów pewnie. Mów tak, by Cię zapamiętali.**

‼Halo Łódź i okolice‼
#**ZAPRASZAMYNAPLAN **📽🎥‼‼

Serdecznie zapraszamy do udziału w
kontynuacji kultowego serialu, dla jednej z platform streamingowych. Plan
będzie wyjazdowy (ok. 100 km), na miejscu gramy pod dachem. Można się zapisywać
na 1, 2 lub 3 dni. 

✅ **KIEDY i GDZIE:**
Wyjazd z ŁODZI (oczywiście powrót w to samo
miejsce, pkt. zbiórki będzie dopiero ustalony).
**30.09 (wt.), 01.10 (śr.), 03.10 (pt.)** ➡ kobiety i mężczyźni.

❇ **ZAPRASZAMY: **🧍‍♀️🧍
Panie i Panów, o każdej możliwej aparycji, w
wieku +16 lat, górnej granicy wieku brak - liczą się chęci i pozytywne🕵
nastawienie do udziału w planie zdjęciowym.

💰**WYNAGRODZENIE **💲 za udział w planie: 100 zł netto/dzień zdjęciowy (UoD, płatne przelewem) + dodatkowo 20 zł netto za podróż tam i z powrotem (Produkcyjnym autokarem ). 🙂

Na planie Produkcja zapewnia: kawę, herbatę,
wodę, bułki i jednodaniowy obiad. A także opiekę medyczną.
—
⬇ **KOMPLETNE ZGŁOSZENIE** zawierające poniższe dane, wyślij:
- komunikatorem WhatsApp/SMS na nr ‪+48 660
543 967;
- lub mailem, z tytułem: „Odjazdowa ŁÓDŹ”:
123cast.film@gmail.com

**‼W mailu / komunikatorze podaj wszystkie**
**poniższe dane, dokładnie wg. tej formatki ⬇:**
—
Imię i nazwisko
Nr tel.
Miejsce zamieszkania
Data urodzenia
Wzrost (w cm)
Waga (w kg)
Rozm. obuwia (w nr EU)
—
Terminy w których mógł(a)byś wziąć udział w
planie filmowym (30.09, 01.10, 03.10).
—
+dołącz koniecznie jako ZAŁĄCZNIK DO MAILA
(bez linku do galerii zdjęć)/wiadomości na WhatsApp:
2x AKTUALNE ZDJĘCIA, zrobione telefonem
komórkowym -> portret i sylwetka: z aktualną fryzurą i wyglądem (zrobione
max. do 3 dni przed ich wysłaniem); bez osób trzecich na zdjęciach, i bez
nakryć głowy oraz bez okularów.
—
Do zobaczenia na planie :)

items.text:
WARSZAWA (ŁÓDŹ - transport do Warszawy)
4, 6 i 7 października
film fabularny

Zapraszamy Was na plan kolejnego filmu. Tym razem "JAN BO" czyli film biograficzny o Janku Borysewiczu. 
Pana nie trzeba na pewno przedstawiać 😎

Szukamy Statystów w wieku ok. 17-30 lat, którzy będą chcieli pobawić się z nami przez te 3 dni na scenach koncertu.

Ponieważ gramy lata 80te mamy nieuniknione wytyczne charakteryzacji:

Dla wszystkich:
brak tatuaży w widocznych miejscach (ręce również, na nogach u pań też odpadają)
bez tuneli w uszach
Panowie:
bez wygolonych boków i bez włosów ścinanych maszynką, bez zarostów od barbera
długie włosy super
łysi panowie niestety odpadają
Panie:
paznokcie najlepiej naturalne. Współczesny manicure typu długie, kwadratowe paznokcie niestety odpada. Hybryda również. Krótkie paznokcie malowane na np. na czerwono zwykłym lakierem mogą być
bez permanentnych makijaży, doklejonych rzęs i innych ingerencji współczesnych kosmetologii
TRRANSPORT DLA STATYSTÓW Z ŁODZI
Stawka: 120 zł dla Statystów na 1 dzień
Stawka: 140 zł dla Statystów na 2 lub 3 dni i dla Statystów z Łodzi
Przymiarki stacjonarne w Warszawie na Chełmskiej: 2 lub 3.10 do wyboru - płatne dodatkowo 60 zł
Przymiarki online - tylko dla Statystów z Łodzi (wysłanie 3 zdjęć w 3 stylizacjach) - płatne dodatkowo 30 zł

ZGŁOSZENIA
Poproszę na adres: ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl
W tytule: JB + wybrane daty
W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta
W załączniku: ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI: tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.
Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.
Panie - bez grama makijażu, w rozpuszczonych włosach tak, żeby widoczna była długość włosów
Panowie - dodatkowo zdjęcie z profilu

items.text:
Halo Kraków i okolice! Do spotu telewizyjnego **poszukujemy:**
* **kobieta z dzieckiem 2-3 letnim**

items.text:
**Frequent, flexible work opportunities for confident, professional performers with a highly popular Children's entertainment company. We need Seasonal Santa, Party Hosts, Princess Performers **

**Pay: £30- £50 per hour depending on role and responsibilities**

At Bunny Business Events, it is coming up to our busiest time of the year and due to high demand we need to expand our team! We are looking for confident performers, party hosts, performing arts students, actors, singers and those who love working with Children. We are expanding our Santa team (candidates need to be age appropriate for this role), princess performers and generic party hosts. We have frequent & consistent part time work available. Our events are located within Greater Manchester, South Manchester, Warrington and Cheshire. Your residence needs to be within comfortable travelling distance of SK9 Postcode.

**If you are interested in applying please contact with your CV and headshot to hello@bunnybusinessevents.co.uk**

Bunny Business - **Social Media Page**

Bunny Business is one of the leading Children's entertainment companies in the North West. With multiple event's a week, ranging from superheroes, princesses, mascots and disco's, we are now looking for reliable, outgoing children's entertainers to join our team!

So what's the gig? Well, you will receive frequent, flexible bookings during weekend, seasonal events and school holidays, hosting and entertaining large groups of children at various different locations. You will be celebrating birthdays, christenings, Easter, Halloween and Christmas events as well as weddings and corporates. All equipment and training is provided by Bunny Business. It is also advantageous if you can represent one of our many characters, whether it be a superhero, princess or a mascot, all of which are provided by us. This role is perfect if you are looking for additional, flexible income to support your current work commitments.

You need to have the ability to command the attention of the room! You will be responsible for ensuring the smooth running of events and parties, providing excellent hospitality and guest services whilst in character.

***To apply you must have the following set of qualities***

* Confident, loud, fun, engaging, humorous and entertaining
* Frequent Weekend availability
* Must drive and provide own transport (travel cost subsidised)
* Must be able to work in a fast-paced environment with multiple interruptions for attention.
* Provide the highest standard of customer service to our clients
* Strong time management skills

**Experience:-** 

* Previous experience in hospitality, performing arts and/or dance or event management is advantageous
* Strong interpersonal skills with the ability to interact with guests of all ages
* Excellent organisational skills to manage multiple tasks effectively
* Ability to work in a fast-paced environment while maintaining a positive attitude
*  A passion for creating enjoyable experiences for guests

This self employed opportunity is fantastic if you are looking for flexible additional income that is lucrative, engaging, fun and inspiring. Join us as a Party Host or seasonal character and be part of a dynamic team dedicated to delivering exceptional guest experiences.

**Shoot Location: **Tengah Plantation Plaza

**Required Hours:** 2 - 3 hours

**Renumeration:** SGD$50

**Please Note:**

- Age range: 30s - 40s

- Singaporeans and PRs only

- Transport and meals not provided

- Will require your own wardrobe, makeup and hair

*Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.*

If interested, please fill in this Google Form: https://forms.gle/vpe7LYDpESyDvd7D9

Thank you!

Poszukuję lektorki do nagrań reklamowych (voiceover), która byłaby zainteresowana stałą współpracą.
Szukam głosu:

kobiecego,

niskiego,

delikatnego,

naturalnego. 

Pasującego do marek z branży beauty/premium. 

Oferuję:

regularne zlecenia przy produkcjach reklamowych,

współpracę długoterminową,

terminowe rozliczenia i partnerskie podejście.

📩 Zgłoszenia (z próbką głosu/demo: Limitowana, letnia edycja już dostępna. Ten sam skład, nowy smak. Poczuj letnie orzeźwienie i sprawdź na primabiotic.pl) proszę przesyłać na adres: konkursy.primabiotic@natubay.pl

Marta 😙

items.text:
Liebe Leute! 🇦🇹 

Die WSI Agentur sucht aktuell für folgende Rollen Darsteller!

Alle weiteren Details finden Sie nachfolgend:

Gesuchte Rolle:
-einen Mann (30-45)

Was wird gedreht/produziert?
•  Social Media Content - Kurzvideos (bis ca. 30 Sekunden mit Sprechrollen) und Bilder (div. Motive)

Aufnahmeort: - Ilz/Steiermark/Österreich 
Zeitraum: - 1.10 oder 2.10. (je nach Wetter)

Gage: - Gagenvorstellung des Darstellers für einen halben Drehtag für die ausgeschriebene Rolle

Erfahrung benötigt:
•  Erste Produktionserfahrung von Vorteil
•  Natürlich freuen wir uns auch über Bewerbungen von Laiendarstellern

Die Bewerbung soll bitte unbedingt enthalten:

•  Aktuelle Bilder - min. 3 unterschiedliche Bilder (Polas - Handyfotos)
•  Kurzes Vorstellungsvideo
•  Kontaktdaten: Name, Geburtsdatum, Telefonnummer, Meldeadresse
•  Gagenvorstellung für einen halben Drehtag für die ausgeschriebene Rolle

Wir freuen uns über Ihre Bewerbung an casting@weshootit.com.

Wir bedanken uns und wünschen schöne Grüße aus Graz!

🎬 Schauspielerin gesucht! 🎬 {No Budget}

Für einen US-Horror-Kurzfilmwettbewerb suche ich noch eine Darstellerin.

📽️ Eckdaten:

Kurzfilm max. 5 Minuten Länge

Fertigstellung bis 13. Oktober

1 Tag Brainstorming/Planung 
1 Drehtag

Ort: Ingolstadt+Umgebung (Bayern)

Spielalter: 18–35 Jahre

Freude am Horror-Genre 

📌 Wichtig
Wir treffen uns zunächst einen Tag zum gemeinsamen Brainstorming.

Bitte melde dich nur, wenn du problemlos nach Ingolstadt kommen kannst.

📬 Interesse?

Dann schicke mir gerne dein Portfolio oder ein paar Infos über dich!
